<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Upper part of a small <rs type="material">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">stele</rs> (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.315</measure>  × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.43</measure>  × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.10</measure>) with back rounded for insertion into a wall. A moulded <rs type="decoration">gable</rs> above contains a <rs type="decoration">round shield</rs> in relief; below, within a moulded panel, a <rs type="decoration">young male figure</rs> in relief; below, within a moulded panel, a <rs type="decoration">young male figure</rs> in relief, holding a <rs type="decoration">sickle</rs> in the left hand; right hand and lower part lost.</p>
</div>
